Our Private room, “The Social Room” can comfortably accommodate up to 45 people seated and up to 100 people for receptions. Woodward Patio boasts outdoor private dining space for up to 50 guests. Please note there is a food and beverage minimum for all private events. If a private event is not what you are looking for, there are several indoor and outdoor patio options available. If you can’t make it to us let us bring some of our delicious catering to you, we now offer off-site catering delivery! Take Virtual Tour ← → Host it here: Whatever the event, we've got you covered. Here are just a few of the events that we can host.
